It seems, that you are looking not for *anonymous* object but for [ExpandoObject][1] (which is in fact an implementation of `IDictionary&lt;string, object&gt;`), e.g.

      using System.Dynamic;

      ...

      dynamic myObject = new ExpandoObject();

      // Compile-time property
      myObject.foo = &quot;abc&quot;;

      // Run-time property
      string propertyName = &quot;bar&quot;;

      (myObject as IDictionary&lt;string, object&gt;).Add(propertyName, 123);

      Console.Write($&quot;foo = {myObject.foo}; bar = {myObject.bar}&quot;);

**Outcome:**

      foo = abc; bar = 123


  [1]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/system.dynamic.expandoobject?view=netframework-4.8

